description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Tortilla Pie recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.

recipeInstructions.text: Garnish the pie with guacamole, half the sour cream, and diced tomato. Sprinkle with coriander and serve with extra sour cream and tomato on the side.
